name: Sreelatha Meleth

jv_history.partner_name: Mel M Rubin 🧿🧞‍♀️✨ on LinkedIn: I had the absolute pleasure of guesting on Freeman Beals ☀️ podcast
jv_history.source_quote: I had the absolute pleasure of guesting on Freeman Beals ☀️ podcast last week - here’s 2 mins from the hour’s episode. What do you think about what I’ve shared? Since I started to take full ownership

what_you_do: Sreelatha Meleth is a transformational life coach and public health researcher who founded Peace, Power, Presence Now with a mission to help clients overcome self-doubt and step into their highest potential.
who_you_serve: Anyone who longs for a few moments of peace so they can accept, embrace, and then let go of the stressors that keep them from achieving their dreams.
social_proof: Sreelatha Meleth has been featured as a guest on various podcasts.
signature_programs: Peace. Power. Presence. is a 10-part guided meditation course, and Sreelatha Meleth also offers coaching programs and EFT Tapping sessions.
business_focus: Helping clients overcome self-doubt and step into their highest potential through coaching, meditation, and EFT Tapping.
